tagText

public java.lang.String tagText(java.lang.String inDoc,
                                boolean isPrologOutput,
                                boolean isPrologFullOutput)
Tags the incoming text and returns a prolog or "^" list of tagged text.

Parameters:
inDoc - Free text to be tagged by the tagger
isPrologOutput - Flag for Prolog or upCaret formatted output
isPrologFullOutput - Flag for including Degrees of Ambiguity
Returns:
Prolog inspired string of text and tags; NOTE: "^THE_END^" on a line by itself terminator.
